    "We also report H@1, which is the accuracy of the first predicted answer.",
    "For retrieval evaluation, we use Hit@k, which evaluates whether a correct answer is retrieved in the (Sun et al., 2019) 68.1 -45.9 -NSM (He et al., 2021) 68.7 62.8 47.6 42.4 SR+NSM(+E2E) (Zhang et al., 2022a) 69.5 64.1 50.2 47.1 NSM+h (He et al., 2021) 74.3 67.4 48.8 44.0 SQALER (Atzeni et al., 2021) 76.1 ---UniKGQA (Jiang et al., 2023b) 77.2 72.2 51.2 49.1 ReaRev (Mavromatis and Karypis, 2022) 76.4 70.9 52.9 47.8 ReaRev + LMSR 77.5 72.8 53.3 49.7 LLM Flan-T5-xl (Chung et al., 2024) 31.0 -14.7 -Alpaca-7B (Taori et al., 2023) 51.8 -27.4 -LLaMA2-Chat-7B (Touvron et al., 2023) 64.4 -34.6 -ChatGPT 66.8 -39.9 -ChatGPT+CoT 75.6 -48.9 -KG+LLM KAPING (Baek et al., 2023) 73.9 ---KD-CoT (Wang et al., 2023) 68.6 52.5 55.7 -StructGPT (Jiang et al., 2023a) 72.6 ---KB-BINDER (Li et al., 2023) 74.4 ---ToG+Llama2-70B (Sun et al., 2024) 68.9 -57.6 -ToG+ChatGPT (Sun et al., 2024) 76.2 -58.9 -ToG+GPT-4 (Sun et al., 2024) 82.6 -69.5 -RoG-7B (Luo et al., 2024a) 85.7 70.8 62.6 56.2 GNN+LLM G-Retriever (He et al., 2024) 70.1 ---GNN-RAG 85.7 71.3 66.8 59.4 GNN-RAG+RA 90.7 73.5 68.7 60.4 KG-LC SubgraphRAG (Li et al., 2024b) 89.4 -68.6 -GNN-RAG+Route 90.1 -72.4 -GNN-RAG+RA+Route 91.0 * -73.3 * -We denote the best and second-best methods, as well as the best * method with long-context (KG-LC).",
